name: The Workaholic™
description:
Ok, let's go to work... The workaholic!

Twenty-four hours, no time to play
He won't quit, he's addicted to work
I think he's going like a jerk
Working, working, what can you do?
See the life from a different point of view
Waiting in the morning for the bells to chime
I think he's glad it's working time!
The workaholic!
Work your body, baby, work your soul
Keep on workin' workin' to the bone
Work your body, baby, work your soul
I'm a workaholic when I'm on the floor!
Ok, ok, ok, ok
Ok, ok, ok, let's go to work!
The workaholic!
First second third,why you always work?
Messing up your mind with that paperwork
The only thing in his brains above
Is working yo, and that's all
They do it for money, but he for fun
He won't get away until the job is done
No drinkin' drinkin' like an alcoholic
The guy is just a workaholic
The workaholic!
Work your body, baby, work your soul
Keep on workin' workin' to the bone
Work your body, baby, work your soul
I'm a workaholic when I'm on the floor!
The workaholic!
